HEADWORD: Concierge
<hw>Con`cierge"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<def>One who keeps the entrance to an edifice, public or private; a
doorkeeper; a janitor, male or female.</def>⟦br⟧
